## File a Support Ticket

You can file a support ticket [here](https://support.pivotal.io/). Please be sure to provide the [error message](./tshooting-techniques.html#parse-error) from  from `cf service YOUR-SERVICE-INSTANCE`.

To help expedite troubleshooting, please also provide your [service broker logs](./tshooting-techniques.html#access-broker), your [service instance logs](tshooting-techniques.html#access-instance) and [BOSH task output](./tshooting-techniques.html#parse-error), if your `cf service YOUR-SERVICE-INSTANCE` output includes a `task-id`.

